has as much of a noose
around his neck as I will.

1035
01:17:02,584 --> 01:17:04,786
Yes,
but there may be hope.

1036
01:17:04,820 --> 01:17:07,956
You, of all people,
should understand that.
Understand what?

1037
01:17:07,990 --> 01:17:11,460
