01:17:45,627 --> 01:17:47,362
Sweetheart,
I'm so sorry.

1044
01:17:48,363 --> 01:17:50,732
[ Coughing Continues ]

1045
01:17:50,766 --> 01:17:53,201
[ Ebiere ] There's nothing
