1097
01:20:52,147 --> 01:20:54,816
[ No Audible Dialogue ]

1098
01:20:59,721 --> 01:21:03,225
I hereby find you
guilty of murder...

1099
01:21:03,258 --> 01:21:04,759
on all counts.

1100
01:21:04,793 --> 01:21:07,128
You shall be
taken from here...

1101
01:21:07,162 --> 01:21:09,798
