a daughter of the Niger Delta.

1131
01:24:08,910 --> 01:24:11,079
[ Screaming, Wailing ]

1132
01:24:23,258 --> 01:24:25,193
[ Phone Beeping ]

1133
01:24:26,594 --> 01:24:28,563
