What about the people,
goddamn it!

1143
01:25:07,869 --> 01:25:09,471
What about the girl?

1144
01:25:09,504 --> 01:25:11,806
♪♪ [ Singing Continues ]

1145
01:25:16,811 --> 01:25:19,247
This happens to be
