1163
01:26:20,542 --> 01:26:22,744
Stand back!

1164
01:26:22,777 --> 01:26:24,712
Please. Stop.

1165
01:26:24,746 --> 01:26:27,515
I can't do that.

1166
01:26:27,549 --> 01:26:30,151
Hey. Hey.
Listen to me.

1167
01:26:32,220 --> 01:26:34,188
I'm sorry...

1168
01:26:34,222 --> 01:26:36,524
what happened
to your families.

1169
01:26:36,558 --> 01:26:40,762
